<L>__{exterior san francisco streets (top of hill #3) day}
<A>__{mason's humvee, with goodspeed's ferrari close behind, races down a street on the crest of a hill. in the intersection ahead a cable car is turning down the hill. mason's humvee also turns down the hill, but as the humvee rounds the corner an old woman starts crossing the street. mason throws the wheel swerving to avoid her, and the humveeis bumper catches the back of the cable car, dislodging its rear steel wheels from the cable car tpacks. with the front wheels still lodged in the tracks, the cable car becrins to slide sideways. goodspeed's ferrari clears the cable car's sliding back end and sprints after mason's humvee.}
